data.description: This House is Located in a Beautiful Gated Community, and is being Sold by the Original Owners.  This is the Cypress Model Plan from LGI Homes.  With a Grand Private Master Suite Downstairs and Three additional Bedrooms Upstairs.  The Kitchen is Gorgeous with Granite Countertops and Beautiful Wood Cabinets with Energy Efficient Appliances, Washer, Dryer and Refrigerator all Included! A Generously Size Livingroom, and an Open Kitchen with a Large Pantry.  Your Family will enjoy this Beautiful Home with a Fully Fenced Backyard for Great Bar-B-Ques.  Sterling Lakes offers Superior Amenities including a Junior Olypic-Sized Swimming Pool with a Children's Splash pad and a Fitness Center and More!
